<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3147000" xml-lang="en-US" l10n="U" oldref="3"><ahelp hid="sfx/ui/helpcontentpage/HelpContentPage">Displays the main help themes, arranged in a similar way to folders in a file manager.</ahelp></paragraph>
